{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}Every cell also produces waste as a byproduct, and the \b (8)\b0  \b clearance (\f1\lang1049\'ee\'f7\'e8\'f1\'f2\'ea\'e0\f0\lang9 ) \b0 of that waste is the second basic problem that each organ has to solve.\par
